{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-gitdiff","description":"A source plugin for Gatsby that creates Diff nodes from a local git repo.","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-source-plugin","git","diff"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"azeven","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/c253cdf45923228108103516203c96e6"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/antonlegoo/gatsby-source-gitdiff"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-gitdiff\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-gitdiff\" aria-label=\"gatsby source gitdiff permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-gitdiff</h1>\n<p>A source plugin that creates Diff nodes from a local git repo. Each Diff is generated by diffing two adjacent commits using <a href=\"https://git-scm.com/docs/git-diff\">git-diff</a>. A key use case would be to create a change-log section showing the history of changes to your site.</p>\n<p><strong>Important</strong>: Your git repo must be at the root of your Gatsby project. </p>\n<p><strong>Also Important</strong>: No Diff nodes will be produced if you only have one commit in your history (and this will probably produce a “no nodes found” error in graphql queries).</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-gitdiff</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-source-gitdiff`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"./lib/defaultOptions.js\">defaultOptions.js</a> for defaults to each option.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"diffFilter\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"ADM\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                     <span class=\"token comment\">// (string) A = Added, D = Deleted, M = Modified (fed into --diff-filter option of git-diff command)</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"dateFormat\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>  <span class=\"token string\">\"MMM DD, YYYY - h:mm a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// (string) momentjs formatting string, would produce \"Oct 08, 2018 - 12:34 am\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"targetDirectory\"</span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"src/pages\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>         <span class=\"token comment\">// (string) only include diff'ed files in this directory</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"afterCommit\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"017180a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                <span class=\"token comment\">// (string) start comparing after this commit</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"ignore\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> \n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"firstCommit\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                  <span class=\"token comment\">// (bool) ignore the first commit</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"files\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"package.json\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// (string[]) file names to exclude</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"exts\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                       <span class=\"token comment\">// (string[]) file extensions to exclude</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"commits\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"017180a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                <span class=\"token comment\">// (string[]) hashes of commits to exclude</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"diff-node\"><a href=\"#diff-node\" aria-label=\"diff node permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Diff Node</h2>\n<p>The format of a Diff node is as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"node\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"date\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Nov 12, 2018 - 12:31 pm\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// The date of the commit</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Updated home page\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// The commit message (i.e. git commit -m\"Updated home page\")</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"files\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>                          <span class=\"token comment\">// An array of files that have changed</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"src/pages/index.js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// Filepath of file</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"binary\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                <span class=\"token comment\">// Whether the file is a binary</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"type\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"modified\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>             <span class=\"token comment\">// What type of change occured (e.g. added, modified, deleted)</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"changes\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>                    <span class=\"token comment\">// An array of diff-formatted strings</span>\n          <span class=\"token string\">\"-  this\\n+ that\"</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-query\"><a href=\"#how-to-query\" aria-label=\"how to query permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to query</h2>\n<p>A query for Diff nodes would look like:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  allGitDiffCommit {\n    edges {\n      node {\n        date\n        message\n        files {\n          name\n          binary\n          type\n          changes\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>and this would produce a result like:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  &quot;data&quot;: {\n    &quot;allGitDiffCommit&quot;: {\n      &quot;edges&quot;: [\n        {\n          &quot;node&quot;: {\n            &quot;date&quot;: &quot;Nov 12, 2018 - 12:31 pm&quot;,\n            &quot;message&quot;: &quot;Updated home page&quot;,\n            &quot;files&quot;: [\n              {\n                &quot;name&quot;: &quot;src/pages/index.js&quot;,\n                &quot;binary&quot;: false,\n                &quot;type&quot;: &quot;modified&quot;,\n                &quot;changes&quot;: [\n                  &quot; import Image from &#39;../components/image&#39;\\n \\n const IndexPage = () =&gt; (\\n   &lt;Layout&gt;\\n-    &lt;h1&gt;Hi people&lt;/h1&gt;\\n+    &lt;h1&gt;Hello everyone!&lt;/h1&gt;\\n     &lt;p&gt;Welcome to your new Gatsby site.&lt;/p&gt;\\n     &lt;p&gt;Now go build something great.&lt;/p&gt;\\n     &lt;div style={{ maxWidth: &#39;300px&#39;, marginBottom: &#39;1.45rem&#39; }}&gt;\\n&quot;\n                ]\n              }\n            ]\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-gitdiff/","id":"61b4370c-cae1-5a6d-b466-26e6bdb263c8","layout":"plugins"}}